What you need:
 - GNU Make -- <http://www.gnu.org/software/make/make.html>
 - Any cron daemon -- I like Vixie's one -- <ftp://ftp.isc.org/isc/cron/>
 - HTML Tidy -- <http://tidy.sourceforge.net/>
 - GNU Wget -- <http://www.gnu.org/software/wget/>
 - GNU Grep -- <http://www.gnu.org/software/grep/>
 - GNU coreutils -- <http://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/>
 - PHP -- version 5.2 works, 5.3 should --  with libxslt support -- <http://www.php.net/>
 - Web server -- lightttpd, Apache, IIS :D Just about anything capable of serving dynamic PHP content
 - xpath utility from XML::XPath CPAN package -- <http://search.cpan.org/~msergeant/XML-XPath-1.13/XPath.pm>
 - The official Facebook PHP Client Library package -- <http://wiki.developers.facebook.com/index.php/PHP>
   This package contains three directories and a README file, only the php directory is needed
 - API and the Secret Keys -- Get those from <http://www.facebook.com/developers/#/developers/apps.php> and
   put them in config/keys
 - Working brain -- long-term or excessive drinking can and does cause damange to the brain -- Neurological
   damage and memory loss. Some damage can repair itself, but some can become permanent.

That's about it, just start to hack :)

Krtek
